BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Gravel Ride - Carp Relaxed Gravel
DTSTART:20260502T130000Z
DTEND:20260502T160000Z
DTSTAMP:20260428T032428Z
UID:https://obcrides.ca/events/3081
CATEGORIES:
DESCRIPTION:<p>For the first Gravel Ride of the season will be a 43 km Carp Relaxed Gravel - Mix of great gravel/paved roads and scenery. Tires: 32mm (but 28s will do in a pinch). This ride provides an introduction to gravel riding and an opportunity for seasoned gravellers to reconnect as well as stretch their legs after a long winter.</p>
LOCATION:https://maps.app.goo.gl/i6aSk1owVohAbUhk8
