BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Women’s Morning Pink Hill Repeats
DTSTART:20260513T120000Z
DTEND:20260513T130000Z
DTSTAMP:20260428T032428Z
UID:https://obcrides.ca/events/3378
CATEGORIES:
DESCRIPTION:<p><strong>Hello to our 2026 OBC Women Members!&nbsp\;</strong></p><p>Ready to start your Wednesdays with a boost?</p><p>Join us for our morning\, oh so fun<strong>&nbsp\;</strong>Pink Lake Hill climbs&nbsp\;on&nbsp\;Wednesday mornings.</p><p>We meet at&nbsp\;8:00 a.m.&nbsp\;at the&nbsp\;Gamelin P3 parking lot&nbsp\;(the main entrance to the Park).</p><p> <strong>We're going to try starting slightly later this year\, but please let us know (</strong><a title="" href="mailto:sara.sheridan@ottawabicycleclub.ca"><strong>sara.sheridan@ottawabicycleclub.ca</strong></a><strong>) if you prefer an earlier start time\, we can make a 7:30am start on Fridays instead. But you gotta let us know! </strong></p><p>We’ll begin with&nbsp\;1–2 hill repeats&nbsp\;and gradually build up over the summer. Occasionally\, we’ll mix it up with a fun loop from&nbsp\;P3 up to Pink Lake Hill\, down to&nbsp\;Mine Road\, and back to P3.</p><p>Our ride leader is Athena Q</p><p>Registration closes Tuesday night at 6pm\, so don't miss out!</p><p>Signed up but can’t make it? No worries — you have a few options. You can either withdraw through the&nbsp\;<a title="" href="http://obcrides.ca/">obcrides.ca </a>website or just let Athena know (613-552-8572))!!</p><p>Can’t wait to ride with you! 🚴‍♀️✨</p><p>#OBCwomenonbikes</p>
LOCATION:https://www.google.com/maps/place/Stationnement+P3+Parc+de+la+Gatineau+%2F+Parking+Lot+P3+Gatineau+Park/data=!4m7!3m6!1s0x4cce031e372c65c9:0x8af8ead2086e95f8!8m2!3d45.4405657!4d-75.7615835!16s%2Fg%2F1
URL:https://obcrides.ca/events/3378
END:VEVENT
