SUMMARY:Sunday Ride 25-06-07  -  CANCELLED DUE TO RLCT
DTSTART:20260607T160000Z
DTEND:20260607T170000Z
DTSTAMP:20260428T032428Z
UID:https://obcrides.ca/events/3284
CATEGORIES:
DESCRIPTION:<p>No Sunday ride today due to the Rideau Lakes Cycle Tour.</p>
URL:https://obcrides.ca/events/3284
END:VEVENT
